FBIS4-7112 "dreas082__a94021" FBIS-EAS-94-082-A Daily Report 28 April 1994 ANNEX Mongolia Preparations Slow for Spring Sowing Campaign Preparations Slow for Spring Sowing Campaign OW2704123994 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1210 GMT 27 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW2704123994 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME English BFN [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 27 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- According to the Ministry of Food and Agriculture the preparations for the spring sowing campaign of the year 1994 are slowing down. As of today just about 4864 percent [figure as received] of the agricultural equipment and machineries are ready for exploitation. Moreover in many farms of the Bayanulgii and Bayanhongor Aimags in the western part of Mongolia the repairing of such techniques and machineries is not being started yet. The delay in repairing tractors, combines and other agricultural machineries is connection with the lack of spare parts and financial difficulties.
